sequenceDiagram
Client ->> Server: (req) GET / HTTP/1.1 OK
Server ->> Client: (res) sendFile / index.html 

Client ->> Server: (req) GET /boards HTTP/1.1 OK
Server ->> DB: board-list 데이터 줘
DB ->> Server: Params (리턴 데이터)
Server ->> Client: (res) render(Params) / list.html (SSR)

Client ->> Server: (req) GET /write HTTP/1.1 OK
Server ->> Client: (res) sendFile / write.html 
Client ->> Client : 입력 폼 작성 후 Submit
Client ->> Server: POST /boards/write HTTP/1.1 OK
Server ->> DB: INSERT INTO BOARDS (board.push)

Server ->> Client: (res) redirect /board
